Keller Williams Realty Boston-Metro | Back Bay

description: Welcome to 169 I Street, a quintessential South Boston brick row house. This offering represents a unique opportunity for strong positive cashflow in a fully leased, turn-key, asset through 8/31/2025. Meticulously renovated in 2017, each unit features modern kitchens and bathrooms with mini split heating/cooling, all while maintaining the original Southie charm with exposed brick. Rent of $12,300 per month gross is effective September 1st, 2024. Current rents of $12,000 per month gross. Initial showings will be limited to Unit 1 and basement with review of Unit 2 and 3 with accepted offer.
